This paper focuses on developing parallel algorithms for risk analytics using many-core hardware accelerators such as Intel Xeon Phi and NVIDIA GPU. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Computer Engineering (cs.CE), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Numerical Analysis (cs.NA), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
